---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Spring Integration
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Facilitates the implementation of integration solutions in applications that are
- scalable
- asynchronous
- event driven
- microservices
- loosely coupled components
- separation of concerns
- shared systems

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Asynchronous Messaging
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- generic wrapper for any Java object
- consists of headers and a payload
need to deal with concurrency, multithreading, speed, latency,
high availability, fault tolerance, etc.